{{Infobox person | name = Ethem Sancak | image = | image_size = | birth_date = 1958 | birth_place = [[Siirt]] , [[Turkey]] | restingplace = | nationality = Turkish | residence = [[Siirt]], Turkey | occupation = [[Businessman]] | website = }}
'''Ethem Sancak''' (born 1958, [[Siirt]])<ref>''[[Vatan]]'', 8 November 2008, [http://haber.gazetevatan.com/Ergenekon_iddianamesinde_Ethem_Sancak_korundu_mu_207710_1/207710/1/gundem Ergenekon iddianamesinde Ethem Sancak korundu mu?]</ref> is a Turkish businessman considered to have "close ties to President of Turkey [[Recep Tayyip Erdoğan]]".<ref name=HDN/> He completed his primary and secondary education in [[Siirt]]. He graduated from [[Istanbul University]]'s Faculty of Business Administration. Following graduation he worked as a journalist between 1976-1978.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gazetecileronline.com/newsdetails/11416-/GazetecilerOnline/aksam-ve-sky39i-akp-medyasi-mimarina-sattilar |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2014-11-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129033603/http://www.gazetecileronline.com/newsdetails/11416-/GazetecilerOnline/aksam-ve-sky39i-akp-medyasi-mimarina-sattilar |archivedate=2014-11-29 |df= }}</ref>
Ethem Sancak was the owner of the [[Star Media Group (Turkey)|Star Media Group]] from 2004 to 2009, giving its ''[[Star (Turkish newspaper)|Star]]'' newspaper a more pro-[[Justice and Development Party (Turkey)|Justice and Development Party]] (AKP) line.<ref name=HDN>[[Hurriyet Daily News]], 8 June 2010, [http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/pressing-for-freedom-the-rise-of-a-partys-partisans.aspx?pageID=438&n=part-v-the-rise-of-a-party8217s-partisans-2010-06-08 Pressing for freedom: The rise of a party's partisans]</ref><ref>haberler.com, 30 May 2013, [http://en.haberler.com/turkey-approves-50-pct-sale-of-star-media-to123456789-278241/ Turkey Approves 50 Pct Sale Of Star Media To Azerbaijan's SOCAR]</ref> In early 2013 he was listed by [[Forbes]] as the 43rd richest person in Turkey.<ref>gazeteport.com.tr, 19 April 2013, [http://www.gazeteport.com.tr/haber/132111/dedenin-kemiklerini-sizlattin "Dedenin kemiklerini sızlattın"]</ref>
