He has written for ''[[The Jerusalem Post]]'',<ref name=GinzbergJPostSEO>{{cite web|last=Ginzberg|first=Issamar|title=Tips for entrepreneurs: The scoop on SEO|url=http://www.jpost.com/Business/Commentary/Tips-for-entrepreneurs-The-scoop-on-SEO-340256|work=Tips for Entrepreneurs|publisher=Jerusalem Post|accessdate=24 March 2014|date=1 January 2014}}</ref><ref name=LynchDudleyTangowiththeLingo>{{cite web|last=Lynch|first=Dudley|title=TANGO WITH THE LINGO: WHERE THEY’RE TALKING ABOUT MAKING THE LEAP!|url=http://www.braintechnologies.com/blog/2013/05/issamar-ginzberg-and-the-leap/|work=Leap Psych|publisher=Brain Technologies Corporation|accessdate=3 April 2014}}</ref><ref name=JPostGinzberg>{{cite news|last=Ginzberg|first=Issamar|title=Tips for Entrepreneurs: The emperor’s new clothes|url=http://www.jpost.com/Business/Commentary/Tips-for-Entrepreneurs-The-emperors-new-clothes|accessdate=3 April 2014|newspaper=Jerusalem Post|date=4 September 2012|location=Jerusalem}}</ref> ''[[Hamodia]]'',<ref>{{cite news|last1=Ginzberg|first1=Issamar|title=Why Strangers Are Better Than Friends|url=http://www.issamar.com/wp-content/uploads/20141001_XHM_FBY_PG0551.pdf|work=Hamodia|issue=FEATURES|date=1 October 2014|quote=A big mistake many of us make is assuming that if we are going into business, we should look for who we know in that business.}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Ginzberg|first1=Issamar|title=Copywriting and TRWN The most important business formula you’ve never come across|url=http://www.issamar.com/wp-content/uploads/20140923_XHM_FBY_PG058-11.pdf|issue=FEATURES|publisher=Hamodia|date=23 September 2014}}</ref> and ''The English Update''.<ref name="EnglishUpdateGinzberg">{{cite web|last=Ginzberg|first=Issamar|title=Issamar’s Blog|url=http://www.teu.co.il/issamars-blog/|work=English Update|publisher=The English Update|accessdate=25 March 2014}}</ref><ref name="GinzbergEnglishUptateMag">{{cite web|last=Ginzberg|first=Issamar|title=Kratzmich Sales All Year Long|url=http://www.joomag.com/magazine/the-english-update-issue-164-165/0452923001394108876?page=8|work=English Update Magazine|publisher=English Update|accessdate=25 March 2014}}</ref> He has written several books, including ''How Marketers Mess With Your,'' ''Marketing Secrets that Are Used to Get Your Attention'' and ''How To Use Them To Your Advantage''.<ref name=GinzbergHowMarketersMess>{{cite book|last=Ginzberg|first=Issamar|title=How Marketers Mess WIth Your....: Marketing Secrets that Are Used to Get Your Attention... and How To Use Them To Your Advantage [|date=15 June 2010|publisher=Create Space|location=New York|isbn=1452889848|url=https://www.amazon.com/How-Marketers-Mess-Your-Marketing/dp/1452889848/ref=sr_1_4?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1395774370&sr=1-4&keywords=issamar+ginzberg}}</ref><ref name=AmazonGinzbergHeyEntrepreneur>{{cite web|last=Ginzberg|first=Amazon|title=Hey Entrepreneur! You Need to Read This Book, So Buy It Today!|url=https://www.amazon.com/Entrepreneur-Need-Read-This-Today-ebook/dp/B005DO53O6/ref=la_B003UM74YA_1_2?s=books&ie=UTF8&qid=1395771899&sr=1-2|work=Amazon Book Profile|publisher=Amazon|accessdate=25 March 2014}}</ref> Ginzberg wrote the foreword to ''Everything You Need to Know About Buying Real Estate in Israel by Shia Getter''.<ref name=GetterShiaEverythingYouNeed>{{cite book|last=Getter|first=Shia|title=Everything You Need to Know About Buying Real Estate in Israel|date=10 Feb 2014|publisher=Feldheim|location=New York|isbn=978-1-59826-049-6|url=http://www.feldheim.com/authors/getter-shia/everything-you-need-to-know-about-buying-real-estate-in-israel.html}}</ref><ref name=GinzbergGetterJpost>{{cite web|last=Ginzberg|first=Issamar|title=What the Czech Republic can teach you about success|url=http://www.jpost.com/Business/Commentary/What-the-Czech-Republic-can-teach-you-about-success|work=JPost|publisher=Jerusalem Post|accessdate=25 March 2014}}</ref><ref name=MaruchMillerGinzberg>{{cite news|last=Maruch Miller|first=Rochelle|title=The Media Is The Message|u